# Local Terraform directories and lock files
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# Backend config and tfvars hold real secrets / subscription ids
**/backend.hcl
**/terraform.auto.tfvars
**/terraform.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars

# Terraform state (we use remote state, but ignore local copies just in case)
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log

# Plan output
**/*.tfplan

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
